If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : feedback@hekr.me

Amazon Alexa and the Wisen smart home products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to open or close the plug. 
There’s no need to go to the plug to control your plug switch - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your Wisen products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Wisen" App in android or iOS App market;
(2). Register one Wisen account in our "Wisen" App;
(3). You need to have some Wisen smart home devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Wisen" App and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Wisen" skill;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,iOS or Amazon App market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" App;
(7). Search "Wisen" skill from the "Alexa" App skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Wisen", and you'll be navigated to Wisen login page;
(9). Input your Wisen account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,discover my devices.”
“Alexa,turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,dim the bedroom light to 50%.”


Currently this skill supports products:
smart plug,
smart bulb, 
smart heater....
